108
00:05:52,382 --> 00:05:55,287
Alright, you must have been tired all these days.

109
00:05:55,287 --> 00:05:56,931
Go back early to rest

110
00:05:56,931 --> 00:05:58,330
Yes

111
00:05:58,909 --> 00:06:00,239
