113
00:06:01,873 --> 00:06:04,013
You should take the medicine before reading the officers' reports

114
00:06:16,245 --> 00:06:17,176
Su Pei Sheng

115
00:06:18,693 --> 00:06:19,701
I'm here

116
00:06:19,701 --> 00:06:20,794
Follow me for a walk

117
00:06:21,223 --> 00:06:22,439
Yes

118
00:06:24,227 --> 00:06:26,303
