123
00:06:46,094 --> 00:06:47,877
Still not coming? I'm talking to you

124
00:06:49,022 --> 00:06:51,600
My Xiao zhu is Huan Lingering at the Palace of Shattered Jade

125
00:06:52,752 --> 00:06:54,923
Is there any Lingering that dress so simply?

126
00:06:59,009 --> 00:07:00,526
