130
00:07:12,061 --> 00:07:14,949
Promise Yu shi greeting Huan Lingering

131
00:07:15,372 --> 00:07:16,511
Good morning, Promise Yu

132
00:07:17,671 --> 00:07:19,566
Are you in the mood of taking a walk?

133
00:07:20,786 --> 00:07:22,207
I have to serve the Emperor

134
00:07:22,207 --> 00:07:24,687
