135
00:07:25,452 --> 00:07:28,613
However, I have some words to advice Lingering Huan

136
00:07:29,457 --> 00:07:32,229
If you're sick, you shouldn't come out

137
00:07:33,228 --> 00:07:36,587
You should avoid spreading bad fortune to others and getting the blamed for it.

138
00:07:37,262 --> 00:07:38,639
Thank you for your advice

139
00:07:39,535 --> 00:07:42,030
I however also have something to tell you

140
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:45,935
Not sure if Lingering Huan have any brilliant words for me?

141
00:07:47,022 --> 00:07:49,880
I hear that the Emperor always like people that are refined and courteous

142
00:07:50,564 --> 00:07:52,260
Yet when Promising Yu saw me

143
00:07:52,876 --> 00:07:54,325
