145
00:07:58,764 --> 00:08:00,170
Let's do it like this

146
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:01,551
I'll have my maid do the greeting first

147
00:08:01,551 --> 00:08:03,814
for you to learn

148
00:08:04,436 --> 00:08:05,381
Yes

149
00:08:07,129 --> 00:08:08,449
Promising, please have a look

150
00:08:10,223 --> 00:08:12,477
Promising Yu shi greeting Lingering Huan

151
00:08:12,477 --> 00:08:14,377
Wish Lingering Huan happiness and peace

152
00:08:15,476 --> 00:08:17,410
I normally hear sisters in the palace praise Promising Yu's intelligence

153
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:18,774
can learn with one look

154
00:08:19,347 --> 00:08:20,425
Then, Promising

155
00:08:20,425 --> 00:08:22,063
please follow Liuzhu's model

156
00:08:22,063 --> 00:08:23,701
