157
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:27,116
You at most are a no-favor Lingering

158
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:28,972
Now you want me, a Xiao zhu,

159
00:08:28,972 --> 00:08:31,126
to formally greet you?

160
00:08:31,126 --> 00:08:31,712
Do you deserve that?

161
00:08:32,601 --> 00:08:34,351
Xiao zhu, Lingering Huan's status

162
00:08:34,351 --> 00:08:37,027
is really above yours, Xiao zhu

163
00:08:37,713 --> 00:08:39,483
You're a servant that eat the apple tree and protect the pear tree

164
00:08:42,272 --> 00:08:44,714
Do you really think that

165
00:08:44,714 --> 00:08:47,547
role order truly follows status?

166
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:51,494
Whoever the Emperor favors has a higer status.

167
00:08:52,699 --> 00:08:54,270
Otherwise, even if her status is high,

168
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:56,395
she is still a lowly woman

169
00:08:57,114 --> 00:08:59,517
Furthermore, your status

170
00:08:59,517 --> 00:09:02,697
is only higher than mine by just a little bit.

171
00:09:02,697 --> 00:09:04,496
You base on what to order me around?

172
00:09:05,843 --> 00:09:07,738
If it's me who orders

173
00:09:07,738 --> 00:09:12,413
