174
00:09:13,304 --> 00:09:14,567
Greeting your Majesty

175
00:09:19,763 --> 00:09:22,022
Your Majesty, why are you here?

176
00:09:22,645 --> 00:09:24,077
Then why are you here?

177
00:09:25,756 --> 00:09:28,630
I hear that your Majesty recently like to visit the Royal garden

178
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:30,721
thinking that the view must be charming

179
00:09:30,721 --> 00:09:32,946
so I also take a walk here

180
00:09:33,165 --> 00:09:34,814
These aren't honest words

181
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:40,613
I only wish to always be by your Majesty's side

182
00:09:41,201 --> 00:09:43,372
How can you know where I'm going to so well?

183
00:09:49,646 --> 00:09:51,414
Xiao zhu, xiao zhu

184
00:09:54,425 --> 00:09:56,561
Greeting your Majesty

185
00:09:56,561 --> 00:09:57,800
Wish you happiness and peace

186
00:09:57,948 --> 00:09:59,329
Wish you happiness and peace

187
00:09:59,858 --> 00:10:01,074
I

188
00:10:01,696 --> 00:10:04,617
that day didn't intentionally broke my promise and came late

189
00:10:06,376 --> 00:10:08,507
These days although I was sick

190
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:10,539
I still missed you

191
00:10:11,522 --> 00:10:13,662
Did you come here again to wait for me?

192
00:10:17,999 --> 00:10:19,122
Raise

193
00:10:19,738 --> 00:10:22,092
Help you Xiao zhu. Her body is weak

194
00:10:23,004 --> 00:10:23,877
Xiao zhu

195
00:10:25,982 --> 00:10:28,137
Your bad habit hasn't changed

196
00:10:28,652 --> 00:10:31,318
Look like last time the Empress Dowager punished you too lightly

197
00:10:32,351 --> 00:10:34,295
Your Majesty, I know my fault

198
00:10:35,325 --> 00:10:36,659
Today I was ignorant

199
00:10:36,659 --> 00:10:38,522
