201
00:10:41,715 --> 00:10:44,151
Your Majesty please forgive me this time

202
00:10:50,391 --> 00:10:52,346
I'm little sister today commit a horrible mistake

203
00:10:52,346 --> 00:10:54,790
don't dare to ask for your forgiveness

204
00:10:55,094 --> 00:10:59,065
only ask Lingering to think about the fact that we both serve the Emperor

205
00:10:59,065 --> 00:11:00,712
please ask his Majesty to spare my life

206
00:11:06,372 --> 00:11:09,612
Your Majesty, knowing the mistake and fixing it, nothing is better

207
00:11:10,694 --> 00:11:13,414
I think Promising Yu truly know her fault

208
00:11:14,699 --> 00:11:15,775
Your Majesty please forgive her

209
00:11:16,536 --> 00:11:19,558
Since Lingering Huan has already spoken for you

210
00:11:20,474 --> 00:11:22,745
then I cannot let her down

211
00:11:24,882 --> 00:11:27,303
But you never reflect your fault, it's really annoying

212
00:11:28,306 --> 00:11:29,353
Su Pei Sheng

213
00:11:31,964 --> 00:11:33,726
I'm here

214
00:11:33,726 --> 00:11:36,502
Remember, demote Yu shi to Servant Lady

215
00:11:37,321 --> 00:11:38,672
pack her things out of the Palace of Essence

216
00:11:38,672 --> 00:11:41,358
send her to where I cannot see her

217
00:11:43,314 --> 00:11:44,103
Your Majesty

218
00:11:44,103 --> 00:11:45,488
Didn't you say

219
00:11:45,488 --> 00:11:48,194
The status of Lingering Huan is only higher than that of you just a little?

220
00:11:49,197 --> 00:11:52,795
I now promote Lingering to Precious

221
00:11:53,839 --> 00:11:56,508
Your Majesty, promoting Lingering Huan without having her be with you first

222
00:11:56,508 --> 00:11:58,448
I'm afraid it's against the rule

223
00:11:58,448 --> 00:12:00,864
You're doing more and more good things now

224
00:12:00,864 --> 00:12:02,874
even dare to question my order

225
00:12:03,304 --> 00:12:04,473
Your servant don't dare to

226
00:12:05,238 --> 00:12:06,290
I'll go inform your order immediately

227
00:12:08,739 --> 00:12:10,268
Are you so happy

228
00:12:10,268 --> 00:12:11,752
that you've forgotten to thank me?

229
00:12:15,045 --> 00:12:17,430
Firstly, I have made no contribution to the nation

230
00:12:18,048 --> 00:12:19,220
Secondly, I am not of royal blood

231
00:12:19,766 --> 00:12:22,518
Truly...don't dare to receive such a great honor from your Majesty

232
00:12:23,413 --> 00:12:26,058
If I say you can, then you can.

233
00:12:26,058 --> 00:12:28,579
Raise. Kneeling every now and then

234
00:12:28,579 --> 00:12:30,545
don't even think for your body

235
00:12:34,442 --> 00:12:37,152
Mistress Yu, please go back

236
00:12:44,057 --> 00:12:45,211
I'll take my leave

237
00:13:03,962 --> 00:13:05,464
What now? Scared?

238
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:28,504
Your palm is all wet. Are you scared?

239
00:13:36,949 --> 00:13:38,099
You're the Emperor

240
00:13:38,766 --> 00:13:41,720
Before you weren't scared, you had a guts

241
00:13:43,726 --> 00:13:46,930
Before I didn't know you're the Emperor, but now I know.

242
00:13:48,202 --> 00:13:49,776
Your Majesty's magnificence echoes everywhere

243
00:13:50,425 --> 00:13:53,187
I'm just an insignificant woman; I'm unable to not feel fearful

244
00:13:54,232 --> 00:13:55,518
Fear will cause restrain feeling

245
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:58,508
Feeling restrain will turn the relationship into that of the king and officer

246
00:13:59,801 --> 00:14:02,863
That day there was a storm. I didn't intentionally miss our meeting

247
00:14:03,694 --> 00:14:06,115
In only a few more steps I would reach the Royal garden

248
00:14:06,115 --> 00:14:10,833
But the Empress Dowager called for me to the Palace of Health

249
00:14:12,055 --> 00:14:13,833
When I came back to the Royal garden

250
00:14:13,833 --> 00:14:16,540
beauty was no longer here

251
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:18,479
