252
00:14:18,479 --> 00:14:20,558
Is your health getting better?

253
00:14:21,230 --> 00:14:24,078
Am I not soundingly standing here

254
00:14:24,078 --> 00:14:26,232
talking to you?

255
00:14:27,137 --> 00:14:28,308
I'm senseless

256
00:14:28,851 --> 00:14:29,971
Caring causes confusion

257
00:14:32,529 --> 00:14:35,008
Then I thought back. That day it was raining heavily

258
00:14:35,008 --> 00:14:37,036
You were still in recovery

259
00:14:38,035 --> 00:14:39,743
You might cannot come

260
00:14:41,286 --> 00:14:44,867
Truthfully, that day I also kept my promise

261
00:14:44,867 --> 00:14:46,211
Really?

262
00:14:46,952 --> 00:14:49,703
Then you were in the rain. Did you get sick?

263
00:14:50,281 --> 00:14:51,495
Thank you for your caring

264
00:14:52,557 --> 00:14:55,884
I'm also soundingly standing here talking to you

265
00:14:57,598 --> 00:14:58,885
That's good then

266
00:14:59,994 --> 00:15:02,782
