267
00:15:02,782 --> 00:15:04,228
your health must be weaker than normal

268
00:15:05,439 --> 00:15:09,439
Your Majesty, why did you lie to me?

269
00:15:09,756 --> 00:15:10,750
It's not lying

270
00:15:11,785 --> 00:15:13,267
I just don't want that

271
00:15:14,493 --> 00:15:16,896
don't want you because of the status, fear of me

272
00:15:17,854 --> 00:15:20,421
obey me, flatter me

273
00:15:21,083 --> 00:15:24,541
Even more, I don't want to become a lonely person because of my status

274
00:15:24,541 --> 00:15:26,946
without even a confidante

275
00:15:28,145 --> 00:15:30,202
I and your Majesty haven't known much about each other

276
00:15:30,837 --> 00:15:32,663
I dare not be your confidante

277
00:15:34,384 --> 00:15:37,515
I like you becauce of your true nature

278
00:15:38,442 --> 00:15:40,217
If you were like other people

279
00:15:40,969 --> 00:15:44,008
I wouldn't have treasured the promise with you so highly

280
00:15:45,846 --> 00:15:48,116
I'm foolish

281
00:15:48,116 --> 00:15:49,659
I couldn't see anything

282
00:15:50,776 --> 00:15:53,759
I purposely hid it from you. How could you know?

283
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:57,047
Only hard for 17th brother

284
00:15:57,047 --> 00:15:59,329
The many times I had to call him into the palace and jail him here.

285
00:16:00,937 --> 00:16:04,487
Your Majesty's heart is deep and thoughtful. How can I know?

286
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:12,147
Why is your hand so cold?

287
00:16:13,329 --> 00:16:15,647
Is it because of the wind?

288
00:16:16,774 --> 00:16:17,954
I'm not cold

289
00:16:18,549 --> 00:16:20,166
You've been here for a long time

290
00:16:20,166 --> 00:16:21,460
Let me take you back

291
00:16:23,011 --> 00:16:24,284
Walking is tiring.

292
00:16:24,284 --> 00:16:25,423
I'll carry you

293
00:16:25,819 --> 00:16:26,886
I don't dare to

294
00:16:29,919 --> 00:16:30,968
Why not?

295
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:33,850
Others will talk behind you

296
00:16:34,634 --> 00:16:38,335
I care for the woman I like

297
00:16:39,168 --> 00:16:42,229
If people want to gossip, let them

298
00:17:23,302 --> 00:17:26,587
Greeting the Emperor. Greeting Precious Huan

299
00:17:26,587 --> 00:17:27,902
You guys get the news quite quickly

300
00:17:28,644 --> 00:17:29,903
Your Majesty endowing Xiao zhu

301
00:17:29,903 --> 00:17:31,676
is endowing everyone in the Palace of Shattered Jade

302
00:17:31,676 --> 00:17:33,345
We sevants all gladly receive your Majesty's generousity

303
00:17:33,983 --> 00:17:34,692
Raise

304
00:17:34,692 --> 00:17:36,420
Thank you your Majesty

305
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:38,628
You're very good at speaking also. What's your name?

306
00:17:38,628 --> 00:17:40,992
I'm Liuzhu, servant from home of Xiao zhu

307
00:17:41,984 --> 00:17:45,077
Really like mistress like servant

308
00:17:47,506 --> 00:17:48,613
Thank you for your praising

309
00:18:02,872 --> 00:18:04,005
My hands are tired

310
00:18:05,444 --> 00:18:07,639
Are your Majesty saying I'm heavy?

311
00:18:08,382 --> 00:18:10,519
You're not heavy

312
00:18:10,519 --> 00:18:12,412
It's because I'm afraid if I hold you too tightly, you'll be hurt

313
00:18:13,189 --> 00:18:15,370
but if I hold you too loosely, you'll fall

314
00:18:16,052 --> 00:18:18,566
Two hands struggle don't know which way to go

315
00:18:18,566 --> 00:18:19,490
therefore they get tired

316
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:22,177
Your Majesty are used to making fun of others

317
00:18:27,574 --> 00:18:29,112
When Precious Huan was a Lingering

318
00:18:29,112 --> 00:18:30,810
Were there only you guys who serve her?

319
00:18:30,810 --> 00:18:31,816
Yes

320
00:18:32,287 --> 00:18:33,721
I need quiet time for recovery

321
00:18:34,484 --> 00:18:36,834
so I don't need so many servants

322
00:18:37,797 --> 00:18:38,606
That's not Ok

323
00:18:41,462 --> 00:18:43,875
Who are the maid and eunuch managers here?

324
00:18:44,496 --> 00:18:45,386
Responding to your Majesty

325
00:18:45,386 --> 00:18:48,456
I'm Jin Xi, the manager of the maids here

326
00:18:49,109 --> 00:18:51,495
There's no manager of eunuches at the Palace of Shattered Jade

327
00:18:51,495 --> 00:18:53,815
The old manager of eunuches

328
00:18:53,815 --> 00:18:54,690
Two months ago

329
00:18:54,690 --> 00:18:56,607
was called to worked for Li Pin

330
00:18:58,787 --> 00:19:00,039
This is not a problem

331
00:19:01,984 --> 00:19:04,687
It's not all right to not have a eunuch manager at your place

332
00:19:04,687 --> 00:19:07,904
Tomorrow I'll order the Internal Affairs Authority to select some experienced servants

333
00:19:08,662 --> 00:19:10,693
You choose one to be your manager of eunuches

334
00:19:12,458 --> 00:19:15,094
I gladly receive your Majesty's caring

335
00:19:16,145 --> 00:19:17,823
Actually there's no need to cause too many troubles

336
00:19:18,892 --> 00:19:20,543
I think Xiao Yun Zi is very good

337
00:19:21,524 --> 00:19:24,286
How about promoting him to this role, then training him latter?

338
00:19:24,286 --> 00:19:26,904
Thank you your Majesty! Thank you Xiao zhu!

339
00:19:26,904 --> 00:19:29,601
I'll definitely do by best to serve Xiao zhu

340
00:19:31,099 --> 00:19:33,418
Ok. You say he's good then he's good

341
00:19:34,850 --> 00:19:36,145
Avoid having outsiders

342
00:19:36,145 --> 00:19:37,393
who don't know your style

343
00:19:40,773 --> 00:19:42,534
Your Xiao zhu thinks highly of you

344
00:19:42,534 --> 00:19:43,770
you must work even harder

345
00:19:43,770 --> 00:19:45,258
Yes. I'll obey your order

346
00:19:47,916 --> 00:19:49,515
You're promoted to be Precious

347
00:19:49,515 --> 00:19:50,749
now you need more servants

348
00:19:51,376 --> 00:19:54,080
Tomorrow I'll order the Internal Affairs Authority to select some good servants

349
00:19:55,331 --> 00:19:56,019
Thank you your Majesty

350
00:19:59,153 --> 00:20:00,182
Your Majesty

351
00:20:00,734 --> 00:20:02,600
Zhang Ting Yu wants to see you

352
00:20:03,763 --> 00:20:04,455
I know.

353
00:20:11,383 --> 00:20:13,834
Rest well.

354
00:20:15,014 --> 00:20:16,405
I will come back to see you in a few days

355
00:20:20,636 --> 00:20:22,330
I send Your Majesty off

356
00:20:30,971 --> 00:20:32,241
You know my rules

357
00:20:33,138 --> 00:20:35,239
I know that when practicing your writing,

358
00:20:35,239 --> 00:20:36,522
Niang Niang doesn't like to be disturbed.

359
00:20:36,522 --> 00:20:37,784
But...

360
00:20:37,784 --> 00:20:40,772
Promise Yu has been punished. She has been demoted to servant lady.

361
00:20:41,783 --> 00:20:43,315
His Majesty's intention?

362
00:20:43,315 --> 00:20:44,302
Yes, exactly.

363
00:20:45,094 --> 00:20:47,372
This matter was sorted out faster than I expected.

364
00:20:48,209 --> 00:20:49,855
Have someone watch her. Don't allow her to make a fuss.

365
00:20:49,855 --> 00:20:50,710
Yes

366
00:20:51,224 --> 00:20:53,809
Yushi is frivolous. She wasn't fit to serve His Majesty.

367
00:20:54,658 --> 00:20:56,886
and she does not know caution.

368
00:20:56,886 --> 00:20:57,894
How was she incautious?

369
00:20:58,515 --> 00:20:59,910
She overstepped her bounds

370
00:20:59,910 --> 00:21:02,403
and insulted "Precious Smile"

371
00:21:04,198 --> 00:21:05,544
Has she been promoted to Precious already?

372
00:21:06,413 --> 00:21:08,304
His Majesty must like her?

373
00:21:08,764 --> 00:21:09,936
It seems so

374
00:21:10,304 --> 00:21:12,321
But it is against the Palace rules to skip a rank.

375
00:21:12,321 --> 00:21:14,035
you should talk to His Majesty.

376
00:21:14,035 --> 00:21:16,067
Palace rules were set by the ancestors

377
00:21:16,067 --> 00:21:18,033
Ancestors are Sons of Heaven.

378
00:21:18,033 --> 00:21:19,422
The Emperer is also the Son of Heaven.

379
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:23,065
She is not ordinary; it was going to happen sooner or later

380
00:21:27,072 --> 00:21:28,385
Lu Gong Gong, go well

381
00:21:28,385 --> 00:21:29,635
Many thanks Gong Gong

382
00:21:39,522 --> 00:21:41,021
Greetings Precious Wan

383
00:21:41,021 --> 00:21:42,226
The moment he returned to his study,

384
00:21:42,226 --> 00:21:44,236
His Majesty instructed me to bring you some things.

385
00:21:45,415 --> 00:21:46,251
Thank you for your trouble, Gong Gong

386
00:21:46,251 --> 00:21:48,601
It is servant's honor to serve Precious

387
00:21:48,601 --> 00:21:50,126
Precious, please look

388
00:21:50,126 --> 00:21:52,220
This is silk lace

389
00:21:53,182 --> 00:21:54,466
A pair of 'Jing Tai Lan' bangles

390
00:21:55,005 --> 00:21:56,648
A box of orchid head ornaments inlaid with gold and precious stones.

391
00:21:57,433 --> 00:22:00,069
Two boxes of wishful headdress flowers <br />A wishful beads curtain

392
00:22:00,928 --> 00:22:02,608
Sixteen bolts of silk

393
00:22:03,388 --> 00:22:05,701
The last item, His Majesty specially instructed

394
00:22:05,701 --> 00:22:07,353
that Precious must personally take a look.

395
00:22:18,594 --> 00:22:19,672
Many thanks to His Majesty

396
00:22:20,003 --> 00:22:22,407
His Majesty explains that young mistress has been tending to her illness all this time,

397
00:22:22,407 --> 00:22:23,432
she must feel lonely.

398
00:22:23,432 --> 00:22:26,294
so he is giving this to you in hope that you will smile

399
00:22:27,245 --> 00:22:28,919
I cannot personally thank him because of my illness

400
00:22:28,919 --> 00:22:30,805
Gong Gong, please thank His Majesty on my behalf

401
00:22:31,528 --> 00:22:32,717
Young Mistress is too polite

402
00:22:32,717 --> 00:22:34,909
His majesty knows that young mistress has not fully recuperated yet

403
00:22:34,909 --> 00:22:37,078
Too many visitors will impair young mistress's recovery

404
00:22:37,559 --> 00:22:40,079
Except his majesty and the imperial doctor, no one else is allowed entry

405
00:22:40,079 --> 00:22:42,398
He asks that Cui Gugu take care of this

406
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:45,164
Yes, his majesty is considerate and thorough

407
00:22:45,748 --> 00:22:47,436
Then I take my leave

408
00:22:53,337 --> 00:22:54,190
This afternoon

409
00:22:54,190 --> 00:22:56,190
all the gifts we received will not fit in the storage room.

410
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:56,837
Exactly

411
00:22:56,837 --> 00:22:58,408
- Huan Meimei
- Jiejie

412
00:22:58,408 --> 00:22:59,865
Finally, you can stand out above the others

413
00:23:02,273 --> 00:23:03,320
I pay my respects to Precious Wan

414
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,565
What are you doing?

415
00:23:04,565 --> 00:23:05,777
Are us sisters going to be picky about statuses now?

416
00:23:06,459 --> 00:23:08,016
Mei Jiejie was crazy with joy

417
00:23:08,016 --> 00:23:09,199
She dragged me here as soon as she heard the news

418
00:23:09,199 --> 00:23:11,748
But I still have to follow the rules and be alert

419
00:23:11,748 --> 00:23:14,646
We can't go so far as to have everyone drunk with happiness

420
00:23:15,299 --> 00:23:16,408
Linrong is right

421
00:23:16,408 --> 00:23:17,790
Let's go inside quickly to talk

422
00:23:18,313 --> 00:23:19,081
Let's go

423
00:23:22,168 --> 00:23:23,263
You all keep watch outside

424
00:23:23,263 --> 00:23:24,630
No need to serve us inside

425
00:23:24,982 --> 00:23:25,943
Yes

426
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:29,832
How did Jiejie become Precious Wan so silently?

427
00:23:29,832 --> 00:23:31,186
You hid it the secret so well,

428
00:23:31,186 --> 00:23:33,322
not the slightest news was revealed.

429
00:23:33,715 --> 00:23:35,302
I really didn't mean to hide it

430
00:23:35,302 --> 00:23:38,562
I met the Emperor by chance in the imperial garden

431
00:23:39,176 --> 00:23:41,830
There is a saying "the quiet amazes with a single feat"

432
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:43,289
That is you.

433
00:23:43,875 --> 00:23:45,545
I was sitting in my palace

434
00:23:45,545 --> 00:23:46,581
When I first heard of this,

435
00:23:46,581 --> 00:23:47,889
I thought it was an unfounded rumor!

436
00:23:48,703 --> 00:23:51,343
When his majesty's Su Gong Gong passed down the decree,

437
00:23:51,343 --> 00:23:52,573
we finally believed it.

438
00:23:52,573 --> 00:23:54,241
Then we immediately came over to congratulate Jiejie

439
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:58,060
Only...how many pairs of eyes will be focused on you from now on?

440
00:23:58,060 --> 00:23:59,800
You must be careful

441
00:23:59,800 --> 00:24:00,676
I know

442
00:24:01,306 --> 00:24:03,609
The Emperor values Older Sister

443
00:24:03,609 --> 00:24:05,810
and promoted you even though you haven't served him.

444
00:24:05,810 --> 00:24:08,081
With his majesty's favor,

445
00:24:08,081 --> 00:24:08,989
Jiejie need not be afraid.

446
00:24:10,390 --> 00:24:12,262
I got promoted without serving him

447
00:24:12,262 --> 00:24:14,749
It's not good that his majesty favors me too much.

448
00:24:15,302 --> 00:24:16,756
You hold his favour now

449
00:24:16,756 --> 00:24:18,616
They wouldn't dare do anything to you

450
00:24:19,553 --> 00:24:21,905
We heard that because Yushi humiliated Jiejie,

451
00:24:21,905 --> 00:24:23,181
she was reprimanded by his majesty.

452
00:24:24,156 --> 00:24:25,541
With her as an example,

453
00:24:25,541 --> 00:24:27,697
no one would dare provoke Jiejie anymore.

454
00:24:28,470 --> 00:24:29,767
Promise Yu was at fault

455
00:24:29,767 --> 00:24:31,491
But I'm worried that one day,

456
00:24:31,491 --> 00:24:33,967
I will also inadvertently cause trouble like Promise Yu.

457
00:24:34,822 --> 00:24:36,357
Would my family be implicated?

458
00:24:37,534 --> 00:24:40,466
Now that you are officially favored by his majesty, you have no other road to take

459
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:43,877
At least His Majesty protects you

460
00:24:44,541 --> 00:24:45,986
It's better than having no one.

461
00:24:46,906 --> 00:24:48,006
Jiejie don't worry

462
00:24:49,065 --> 00:24:51,291
The most important thing now is to nurture your health

463
00:24:51,291 --> 00:24:53,068
so that you can become a true Precious.

464
00:24:53,738 --> 00:24:55,137
Lingrong is right

465
00:24:55,137 --> 00:24:56,604
As long as our sisters' hearts are linked,

466
00:24:56,604 --> 00:24:59,137
we will definitely survive in the palace.

467
00:25:10,768 --> 00:25:11,774
What kind of place is this?

468
00:25:11,774 --> 00:25:12,917
Why didn't anyone tidy it up?

469
00:25:14,353 --> 00:25:15,480
Young mistress

470
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:18,537
You can't stay in the Palace of Essence anymore

471
00:25:18,537 --> 00:25:20,097
If his majesty hadn't considered your past affections,

472
00:25:20,097 --> 00:25:22,540
I think you should be sent to the Cold Palace.

473
00:25:23,157 --> 00:25:25,344
You wouldn't have your own room

474
00:25:25,344 --> 00:25:26,838
or be able to keep a servant lady to serve you.

475
00:25:27,511 --> 00:25:29,311
You should not complain about this.

476
00:25:29,311 --> 00:25:31,464
Just settle in.

477
00:25:34,762 --> 00:25:38,470
Gong Gong, please take the trouble to let me see the emperor once

478
00:25:38,470 --> 00:25:40,389
The emperor will definitely forgive me

479
00:25:41,234 --> 00:25:42,160
Young mistress overestimates me

480
00:25:43,263 --> 00:25:45,792
We are all instructed by Xia Gong Gong

481
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:49,302
Young mistress, don't you look down on eunuchs the most?

482
00:25:49,302 --> 00:25:51,189
We're not fit to serve you

483
00:26:01,770 --> 00:26:03,483
Young mistress, don't be upset

484
00:26:06,057 --> 00:26:08,268
How dare you

485
00:26:08,268 --> 00:26:10,819
How dare you

486
00:26:22,501 --> 00:26:24,548
Greetings, Princess of Glory.

487
00:26:24,882 --> 00:26:26,450
Servant came over today

488
00:26:26,450 --> 00:26:28,450
to deliver the monthly salary for Palace of Wings.

489
00:26:31,836 --> 00:26:34,343
It seems heavier than usual

490
00:26:35,215 --> 00:26:36,928
It is as it should be

491
00:26:36,928 --> 00:26:39,749
Everyone, high and low, in the Internal Affairs Authority relies on Niang Niang's care

492
00:26:39,749 --> 00:26:41,799
We should honor you with more filial respect

493
00:26:41,799 --> 00:26:44,045
You are quite filial. Get up.

494
00:26:44,908 --> 00:26:45,745
Thanks Niang Niang

495
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:48,629
Lately his majesty has conferred another Precious title

496
00:26:49,151 --> 00:26:51,173
I'm afraid your Internal Affairs Authority will be busier,

497
00:26:51,173 --> 00:26:52,445
with everyone getting ready.

498
00:26:52,445 --> 00:26:54,557
Many thanks for Niang Niang's concern. We're not busy.

499
00:26:54,557 --> 00:26:57,140
At most, they're only errands for a Precious

500
00:26:57,140 --> 00:26:59,034
Not too much work

501
00:26:59,034 --> 00:27:01,255
That Precious Smile has always remained in obscurity

502
00:27:01,255 --> 00:27:05,602
She must have taken a lot of abuse from your Internal Affairs Authority

503
00:27:06,201 --> 00:27:08,764
She's in favor now

504
00:27:08,764 --> 00:27:10,423
so you have making up to do

505
00:27:10,423 --> 00:27:12,164
Good luck with that

506
00:27:13,032 --> 00:27:15,055
If his majesty hears anything from her,

507
00:27:15,693 --> 00:27:17,576
even I won't be able to help you.

508
00:27:19,645 --> 00:27:21,825
Niang niang please take care of me

509
00:27:23,771 --> 00:27:25,753
How can I take care of you?

510
00:27:26,416 --> 00:27:28,939
You're in charge of tasks for the Internal Affairs Authority

511
00:27:29,862 --> 00:27:32,207
Carefully select people to serve her

512
00:27:38,946 --> 00:27:41,445
Young mistress, Princess of Glory sent over these snacks

513
00:27:41,445 --> 00:27:42,328
Young mistress, have a taste

514
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:46,598
It is said that pastries from Princess of Glory's palace

515
00:27:46,598 --> 00:27:48,139
are better than the Royal Kitchen.

516
00:27:48,139 --> 00:27:49,484
And she doesn't give it away easily.

517
00:27:52,121 --> 00:27:53,248
You may leave.

518
00:27:53,248 --> 00:27:54,270
yes.

519
00:28:03,749 --> 00:28:05,042
These pastries

520
00:28:05,042 --> 00:28:07,789
is indeed better than the Royal Kitchen's.

521
00:28:08,475 --> 00:28:09,684
Mistress should try it.

522
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:15,240
Seeing these pastries

523
00:28:15,903 --> 00:28:17,626
reminds me of the punishment

524
00:28:17,626 --> 00:28:18,696
which crippled Xia Dong Chun

525
00:28:20,056 --> 00:28:23,024
Jing Xi, I'm so scared.

526
00:28:24,265 --> 00:28:26,088
Things can change in an instant here.

527
00:28:27,020 --> 00:28:28,908
Being afraid will not solve anything.

528
00:28:31,263 --> 00:28:32,693
But one thing remains the same.

529
00:28:33,231 --> 00:28:35,609
The word "favor" is still the most important thing.

530
00:28:36,179 --> 00:28:38,801
Too much favour will raise the ire of others.

531
00:28:39,404 --> 00:28:40,579
Too little favour

532
00:28:40,579 --> 00:28:43,382
will give others permission to step on you.

533
00:28:45,007 --> 00:28:46,607
Mistress should understand,

534
00:28:46,607 --> 00:28:47,734
regardless of whether you are in favour or not

535
00:28:47,734 --> 00:28:49,675
you are never free

